<div id="New_Employee_Training" class="center white-text">
  <h1>New Employee Training / Onboarding</h1>
  <div class="container">
    <h4>Whether you are building your new employee training from scratch, or if you want a consult of how to improve your new employee training; I can help breathe life into this for you.  Your employee's first impression of your company comes from your recruiting and training.</h4>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="Product" class="center white-text">
  <h1>Product / Tool Training</h1>
  <div class="container">
    <h4>As all company's innovate and change to keep on top, so does your product training!  Product or tool updates should be delivered differently to new hires and to existing employees - and I can help bring this to both!</h4>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="Soft" class="center white-text">
  <h1>Soft Skill / Behavior Training</h1>
  <div class="container">
    <h4>Some of the most challenging training to deliver and see impact from, is when you are trying to change the behavior or soft skills of an employee.  From my previous success of coaching, training , and mentoring in this area; I can help build a program that will allow you to measure the results.</h4>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="Leadership" class="center white-text">
  <h1>Leadership Training</h1>
  <div class="container">
    <h4>From coaching workshops to time management, I can help build training solutions to help enhance the leaders across your organization.</h4>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="Training" class="center white-text">
<h1>Training Consultant</h1>
<div class="container">
  <h4>Sometimes, you just need a second set of eyes.  I can help provide that for you!  Sometimes the best feedback comes from a neutral party.</h4>
</div>
</div>

<div id="Facilitation" class="center white-text">
  <h1>Facilitation Assistance</h1>
  <div class="container">
    <h4>With over 10 years of training and facilitation experience, I can also lend my hand at delivering your employee training.  This can be done both virtually or in person, let's talk about the options that best fit your need!</h4>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="Trainer" class="center white-text">
  <h1>Trainer Development</h1>
  <div class="container">
    <h4>Many companies want to build their internal talent and promote from within.  This is great for employee satisfaction and for your culture.  However, sometimes the best Subject Matter Experts (SME's) are not always the best trainers.  I can help coach, develop, and mentor your trainer(s) to deliver engaging and impactful training!</h4>
  </div>
</div>

